<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="js" lang="en">

<head>
  <title>Style Guide | Receipts | MyService</title>
  <%- include(partials+"components/styleguide/styleguide-styles-and-scripts") %>
</head>

<body class="uikit-body uikit-grid uikit-refactor">
  <%- include(partials+"components/styleguide/styleguide-header") %>
  <main>
    <div class="container" id="main-content">
      <nav class="uikit-breadcrumbs" aria-label="breadcrumb">
        <ul class="uikit-link-list uikit-link-list--inline">
          <li>
            <a href="/styleguide">Home</a>
          </li>
          <li>Receipts</li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-9">
          <h1>Receipts</h1>
          <h2>Receipt</h2>
          <p>The receipt component is shown at the end of an application. The receipt features a header with a claim ID and submitted date followed by an application/claim
            summary divided by HR's.</p>
          <p>Receipts are generally centered on a page with perhaps an additional page heading.</p>
          <div class="example-box">
            <div class="flex-item flex-item--centred receipt">
              <div class="receipt__heading ">

                <h4 class="right floated margin-below--none margin-above--none padding-below--none ss-align ms-align--right">
                  <b>Claim Id: 123456789</b>
                </h4>

                <h3 class="margin-above--none ss-align">
                  Submitted on 17 Oct 2017
                </h3>

              </div>
              <div class="receipt__content">

                <h2>Free mental health treatment</h2>

                <p>Approved under our
                  <a href="#auth" rel="external" target="_blank">non-liability health care</a> arrangements.</p>

                <hr>

                <h3>Veterans supplement</h3>

                <p>You may be entitled to the
                  <a href="https://www.dva.gov.au/factsheet-is18-veterans-supplement" rel="external" target="_blank">veterans suppliment</a>. If eligible, we will deposit this
                  fortnightly payment into your nominated
                  bank account.
                </p>

                <h4 class="claim-summary__label margin-below--mid">Bank details</h4>

                <p>
                  <b><span class="pt-current-user-name-full">Alex Kirby</span>'s AU
                    <br>Commonwealth Bank account
                    <br>Account number: xxxx xxxx
                    <br>BSB: xxx - xxx</b>
                </p>

              </div>

              <div class="pagination">
                <button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary" onclick="window.location.href = '/auth/claim'">Back to home</button>
                <button class="uikit-btn floated uikit-btn--tertiary">Print</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>An example of this component can be found <a href="/auth/profile/nomrep/view-rep.ejs">here</a>.</p>
          <hr>
        </div>
        <%- include(partials+"components/styleguide/styleguide-sidenav") %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <%- include(partials+"components/styleguide/styleguide-footer") %>
</body>

</html>
